            Spreading awareness about situations within Palestine
            ðŸ¤²
            Palestine is sometimes called the Holy Land. It is a
            sacred place for three major religions: Islam, Christianity,
            and Judaism.
            Palestine is a region in the Middle East. It is in the
            Levant, between the Jordan River and the Mediterranean Sea.
            Many cultures have lived in Palestine through history and
            built their civilizations, such as the Philistines,
            Phoenicians and Arabs.
